Tech Support Greatest Hits Read-only forum with answers to the most commonly asked newbie techsupport questions pulled from all the other forums. Check here for basic Winamp support answers before digging into the forums.

Winamp Technical Support Howzit....Whatzit...what tha...? How to tune up, and keep your Winamp 5 player humming along. Search this Forum to find others who have driven down your road and have advice and tips to help you out.
deppy, DJ Egg, JonnyMac, Mr Jones
Winamp Discussion What is Winamp 5? Why is Winamp 5? How is Winamp 5? All these burning questions and issues discussed within.
Site Design Love it? Hate it? This is the place to give the admins and developers feedback on the winamp.com site itself.
Winamp Wishlist Do you have a great idea about Winamp 5? Let us know and maybe your features will be in the next release!
Winamp Bug Reports Did you find a bug in Winamp 5? Can you reproduce it? Let us know, we'll try to fix it as soon as possible!
Winamp Remote All things Winamp Remote shall hereforth be discussed here!
aguion, akorb, iMacAtOrb, montale127, olivier_t, rafcortina, williamatorb
SHOUTcast Technical Support Something go south with your SHOUTcast? Need tips to get up and streaming. check in here with the experts.
SHOUTcast Discussions Have SHOUTcast questions or suggestions? Want to help a fellow SHOUTcaster or Listener? Come on in!

Nullsoft Streaming Video Discussion and support for NSV. A new video format designed to be easily streamed, support any audio and video codec, and be usable on nearly any platform. WARNING: Beta Software, not for the weak.
General Discussions You wanna talk about something, but don't know where to turn? Chat your heart out here...

Breaking News The forum for all things in the news. Politics, war, international, national, technical, program releases. All the news that's fit to blab about. Now more than before.
Music O'Rama All music all the time. For musicians and fans and critics and engineers and audiophiles and for anyone who's ever wanted to make a loud noise by strumming, blowing or hitting something.

Games Center A small corner of Winamp dedicated to the pursuit of video & computer gaming. Come and shout about your high scores, the bosses you have slayed and most of all tell us how to wrestle the controller away from Jon Ward when he's playing Puzzle Fighter
Movies and Television This is the place for chit chat about the latest movie to the classic black and white cinema, from the silver screen to the television.
The Bitchlist Need a place to rant, vent, spew? Something happening within the Winamp universe you don't like? This is your place to bitch at the injustice and general unfairness of the World.

International Connection Have a problem, suggestion, comment, but you find it easier to express yourself en Fran硩s, auf Deutsch, en Espanol, in Nederlands, in Italiano? Esperanto? This is your space on the Winamp forums.

Skinning Tips and Tricks Need help in drawing and cutting and pasting them thar purty pictures into a Winamp Skin? A read-only forum with answers to the most commonly asked newbie skinning questions pulled from other forums.
Classic Skins The place for all your Winamp Classic Skin lovin'. This is where you can share your favorite skins, get ideas for a new skin, or just get help on building your own...

Modern Skins The home for Winamp Modern Skins. This is where art and code clash! If you get stuck with your Maki (Nullsoft's scripting language) or XML, come on over! If you figure out a clever way to do something, post your solution here!
Arts and Design A general forum for the artistic people in the forums. Design, graphics, art, avatars and other shiny objects.
Skin and Plug-in Rip Reporting for Removal Report ripped skins and/or plugins here for immediate action(removal).
Winamp Development Discussion and help for Winamp plug-ins and add-on development, because shop talk makes for mo bettah tweaking. Threads not development related will be locked.

NSIS Discussion Are you a developer who uses NSIS to distribute your application? Are you a Winamp plug-in developer who wants to use NSIS to distribute your plug-in? Have suggestions for other people like you? This is the place.

AVS A space to talk about everything related to Winamp Advanced Visualization Studio. Look at the pretty lights.... If you have any troubleshooting questions, bugs, or feature requests, submit them to the AVS SUB-Forums instead of this one!

MilkDrop Posting general comments about the MilkDrop plug-in for Winamp here! If you have a bug report or troubleshooting question, a feature request, or want to share a preset you've made, please use that specific SUB-Forums instead of this one!
Other Visualizations There is just more then AVS and Milkdrop. Check out Nullsoft's other free visualizations by Ryan Geiss.
Recycle Bin The forums wasteground. Posts here count towards nothing, your life may be better off without them.
